works.description: Private images of my wife were stolen from my computer and placed on the internet.  The images were taken by me and I am the sole copyright holder on them.  I have never given anyone permission to distribute or post the images online.  The are of a very sensitive and possibly defamatory nature.  Subsequently, I do not have a site to which I can link for their origination in the next box.  However, I do not give anyone the right to place my images online, in a torrent or otherwise.
